---
// src/components/Contact.astro
// 联系我们/志愿者招募组件 - 简洁现代设计
// Contact & Volunteer Recruitment Component - Clean modern design
---

<section
    id="contact"
    class="py-24 px-6 bg-base-100"
>
    <div class="container mx-auto max-w-5xl">
        {/* 标题 - 更大更有力 */}
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
            <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold mb-6">
                寻找<span class="text-chaihuo">同行者</span>
            </h2>
            <p
                class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-base-content/60 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed"
            >
                路线决策优先级 = 场景价值 × 承担意愿
            </p>
            <p class="text-lg text-base-content/50 mt-4">
                我们看重的不仅是场景，更是"一起扛事"的合作精神
            </p>
        </div>

        {/* 志愿者类型卡片 - 简洁两列 */}
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-16">
            {/* 类型1：带真实问题的人 */}
            <div
                class="bg-base-200 rounded-2xl shadow-lg p-8 border-l-4 border-chaihuo hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow border-y border-r border-base-300"
            >
                <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
                    <div
                        class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-chaihuo/10 flex items-center justify-center"
                    >
                        <span class="text-2xl">🎯</span>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold">带真实问题的人</h3>
                </div>
                <p class="text-base-content/70 leading-relaxed">
                    你有待解决的真实问题，并愿意开发"场景"让我们一起寻找解决方案。
                </p>
            </div>

            {/* 类型2：带可落地方案的人 */}
            <div
                class="bg-base-200 rounded-2xl shadow-lg p-8 border-l-4 border-tech-blue hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow border-y border-r border-base-300"
            >
                <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
                    <div
                        class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-tech-blue/10 flex items-center justify-center"
                    >
                        <span class="text-2xl">💡</span>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold">带可落地方案的人</h3>
                </div>
                <p class="text-base-content/70 leading-relaxed">
                    你已有成熟的软硬件方案，希望在真实场景中验证、迭代并寻找应用机会。
                </p>
            </div>

            {/* 类型3：能承载一站的空间 */}
            <div
                class="bg-base-200 rounded-2xl shadow-lg p-8 border-l-4 border-earth hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow border-y border-r border-base-300"
            >
                <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
                    <div
                        class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-earth/10 flex items-center justify-center"
                    >
                        <span class="text-2xl">🏠</span>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold">能承载一站的空间/主理人</h3>
                </div>
                <p class="text-base-content/70 leading-relaxed">
                    你能提供场地、电力等基础支持，并愿意共同组织活动，成为我们在城市的据点。
                </p>
            </div>

            {/* 类型4：愿意长期共建的人 */}
            <div
                class="bg-base-200 rounded-2xl shadow-lg p-8 border-l-4 border-accent hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow border-y border-r border-base-300"
            >
                <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
                    <div
                        class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-accent/10 flex items-center justify-center"
                    >
                        <span class="text-2xl">🤝</span>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold">愿意长期共建的人</h3>
                </div>
                <p class="text-base-content/70 leading-relaxed">
                    你关注长期、复杂的硬核方向（如具身智能、康养机器人），希望深度合作。
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        {/* 参与意愿等级 - 更简洁 */}
        <div class="bg-base-200 rounded-2xl shadow-lg p-8 mb-16 text-center border border-base-300">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-6 text-base-content/80">
                参与意愿等级
            </h3>
            <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
                <span
                    class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-5 py-3 bg-chaihuo/10 text-chaihuo font-medium rounded-full"
                >
                    🔥 愿意共担（场地/组织/人力等）
                </span>
                <span
                    class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-5 py-3 bg-tech-blue/10 text-tech-blue font-medium rounded-full"
                >
                    ✋ 部分承担
                </span>
                <span
                    class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-5 py-3 bg-base-300 text-base-content/70 font-medium rounded-full"
                >
                    👀 纯希望见证基地车
                </span>
            </div>
        </div>

        {/* 主 CTA - 报名问卷 */}
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
            <p class="text-base-content/60 mb-8 text-lg">
                无论你是想邀请基地车到你的城市，还是想成为同行者，欢迎填写报名表
            </p>
            <a
                href="https://jsj.top/f/JW9bBm"
                target="_blank"
                class="btn btn-primary btn-lg gap-3 shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl hover:scale-105 transition-all text-lg px-10"
            >
                <svg
                    xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                    class="h-6 w-6"
                    fill="none"
                    viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                    stroke="currentColor"
                >
                    <path
                        stroke-linecap="round"
                        stroke-linejoin="round"
                        stroke-width="2"
                        d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z"
                    ></path>
                </svg>
                填写报名问卷，成为同行者
            </a>
        </div>

        {/* 社交媒体入口 - 简洁链接风格 */}
        <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center items-center gap-8">
            <a
                href="#"
                target="_blank"
                class="link-arrow text-base-content/70 hover:text-red-500 transition-colors"
            >
                📕 小红书：柴火基地车 <span>→</span>
            </a>

            <div class="dropdown dropdown-top dropdown-hover">
                <label
                    tabindex="0"
                    class="link-arrow text-base-content/70 hover:text-green-500 transition-colors cursor-pointer"
                >
                    💬 微信公众号 <span>→</span>
                </label>
                <div
                    tabindex="0"
                    class="dropdown-content z-10 card card-compact shadow-xl bg-base-100 w-64 p-4 rounded-2xl border border-base-300"
                >
                    <div class="card-body items-center text-center">
                        <p class="font-bold text-base-content">
                            扫码关注公众号
                        </p>
                        <div
                            class="w-40 h-40 bg-white rounded-lg p-2 border border-base-200 flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden relative"
                        >
                            {
                                /* 默认显示本地图片，如果不存在则通过 CSS/JS 处理或用户自行替换 */
                            }
                            <img
                                src="/wechat-qrcode.png"
                                alt="柴火创客空间公众号"
                                class="w-full h-full object-contain z-10 relative"
                                onerror="this.style.display='none'; this.nextElementSibling.style.display='flex';"
                            />
                            {/* 图片加载失败时的占位提示 */}
                            <div
                                class="hidden absolute inset-0 flex-col items-center justify-center bg-base-100 text-base-content/50 text-xs text-center p-2 z-0"
                            >
                                <svg
                                    xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                                    class="h-8 w-8 mb-2 opacity-50"
                                    fill="none"
                                    viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                                    stroke="currentColor"
                                >
                                    <path
                                        stroke-linecap="round"
                                        stroke-linejoin="round"
                                        stroke-width="2"
                                        d="M3 9a2 2 0 012-2h.93a2 2 0 001.664-.89l.812-1.22A2 2 0 0110.07 4h3.86a2 2 0 011.664.89l.812 1.22A2 2 0 0018.07 7H19a2 2 0 012 2v9a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2V9z"
                                    ></path>
                                    <path
                                        stroke-linecap="round"
                                        stroke-linejoin="round"
                                        stroke-width="2"
                                        d="M15 13a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"
                                    ></path>
                                </svg>
                                <span
                                    >请将二维码命名为<br />wechat-qrcode.png<br
                                    />放入 public 目录</span
                                >
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <p class="text-sm text-base-content/60">柴火创客空间</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <a
                href="#"
                target="_blank"
                class="link-arrow text-base-content/70 hover:text-blue-500 transition-colors"
            >
                📚 语雀知识库 <span>→</span>
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
